title: He Started to Tickle Me!
description: Dave has a picture of a woman he think Jenny will look like when she's 50, we try to find a listener that made a bucket list involving KDWB, a new game called Distraction, we audition listeners to come in and be a live studio audience, Narc on your Neighbor, War of the Roses, what's keeping you up at night?, and more!
